help:
Command List:
!les (optional: [Date])
!les week (optional: [Date])
!les morgen
!les add [Date] [Message]
!les ['rm' || 'remove' || 'del' || 'delete'] [Date]
!deadline add [Time + Date] [Vak] [Message]
!deadline ls 
!deadline ['rm' || 'remove' || 'del' || 'delete'] [Time + Date]
!deadline vak
Date is always in this format: day-month.
Time + Date is always in this format: minute-hour-day-month[optional: -year].
